  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Effektivitetsrevision OPC 2019</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Efficiency audit OPC 2019</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Effektivitetsrevision ska g&#xF6;ras av organistationen som under 2019 genomgick en omorganisering. 
Det finns ett behov av att titta p&#xE5; roller
och mandat samt nya rutiner inom organisationen. En upphandling g&#xF6;rs av CIVSAM f&#xF6;r att bed&#xF6;ma organisationens kapacitet samt ge rekommendation kring
eventuella svagbeter och brister som b&#xF6;r hanteras. Revisionen inkluderar &#xE4;ven stickprov p&#xE5; avtalsefterlevnad hos 2 av organisationens samarbetspartner.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Efficiency audit of OPC will be done which in 2019 underwent a reorganization.
There is a need to look at roles
and mandate as well as new routines within the organization. A procurement is done by CIVSAM to assess the organisation&apos;s capacity and to make recommendations about it
any weaknesses and deficiencies that should be addressed. The audit also includes sampling on contract compliance with 2 of the OPC&#xB4;s organisations.</narrative>
  </description>
